Starting with SDK 3.1.200 I experienced the following MSBuild issue:

When you instantiate classes within a MSBuild task from an external assembly via reflection those types don't behave as expected.  
The issue only appears via MSBuild.

Here's a sample project: [MSBuildTaskDemo.zip](https://github.com/dotnet/sdk/files/4399590/MSBuildTaskDemo.zip)

Just execute `run.bat` to reproduce the issue.

If you change `global.json` to an older SDK version, everything works as expected: 
```json
{
  "sdk": {
    "version": "3.1.100"
  }
}
```
